<P>
KNICKS SHOULD CLEAN UP ACT 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Come on Pat Riley, you didn't used to have to win this way. After having just 
witnessed the Knicks-Bulls series, I am left with a feeling of real concern 
regarding the outright dirty tactics used by the Knicks.I don't know how many 
times I saw John Starks, Charles Oakley, Derek Harper and some of the other 
