SCHWARTZ WINS SPEEDWAY MAIN EVENT 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Bobby Schwartz of Costa Mesa won the four-lap scratch main event in the weekly 
speedway motorcycle program Friday at the Orange County Fairgrounds. 
</P>
<P>
 Brad Oxley of San Juan Capistrano was second, Mike Faria of Apple Valley third 
and Don Odom of Redondo Beach fourth. 
</P>
<P>
 Josh Larsen of Balboa won the eight-lap handicap main event. Faria was second, 
Ed Castro of Ojai was third, Andy Northrup of Ontario was fourth and Mark 
Hannah of Newport Beach was fifth. 
</P>
