 Courts across southern China's Guangdong province ordered 33 car thieves 
executed Friday as part of a campaign against car theft, according to an 
official newspaper seen today. 
</P>
<P>
 The Yangcheng Evening News said courts in 14 towns and cities held mass 
sentencing rallies for 101 people accused of car theft and that 33 were 
