want to go," Watson said. 
</P>
<P>
 Two of the four deputies returned fire, Watson said, killing Stephen Mercer. 
</P>
<P>
 Watson said the elder Mercer had accompanied the deputies, who sought to have 
his son evaluated at a veterans hospital. 
</P>
<P>
 The younger Mercer had been involved in a seven-hour standoff with Albuquerque 
police last week and had held off police for 45 minutes on Thursday, Watson 
said. 
