<TEXT>
<P>
 "Batman" credits -- Tim Burton was the director of "Batman" and "Batman 
Returns." Joel Schumacher will direct the upcoming sequel, "Batman Forever," 
while Burton will be executive producer. Wednesday's Morning Report misstated 
Schumacher's affiliation with the "Batman" movies. 
